<D>__{i will get lots of kisses next weekend.}
<P>__{(to john)}
<D>__{we want to take him to the harvest festival in kutztown, where they have the clydesdales.}
<A>__{john thinks about saying something, can't. he watches luke give grace a kiss.}
<C>__{luke}
<D>__{thank you, grandma.}
<A>__{john turns to his father, who stands in the doorway. his father holds out the jacket in silence. john takes it. the airline tickets stick out from the inside pocket. john realizes the tickets have been moved from the bag. he looks at his father, who gazes back at him in silence. john can tell by the look in his father's eye that he knows.}
<C>__{john}
<D>__{bye mom.}
<A>__{they kiss. john's father stands behind him.}
<C>__{george}
<D>__{goodbye.}
